author: @Enhypen_forever357
text:
Dear New Jeans✨💌,
Please don't leave! My heart is breaking at the thought of losing you. You are gems, shining brightly in the K-pop scene. Your talent, passion, and kindness have captured the hearts of fans and artists alike.😭🥺🫂💓🫶🏻
I desperately wish for a better future for you, whether it's finding a new company that truly values and supports you or for your current company to recognize your worth and treat you with the love and respect you deserve.🎀💝⭐🌷
Your artistry inspires countless people, including the talented members of Le Sserafim. Your presence makes a difference, and your departure would leave an unfillable void.❤️😭💓🍥🫶🏻💝
Stay together, dear New Jeans. Your music and love are cherished. Don't go!😭🥺🙏🏻

author: @beeyacht2381
text:
Today, I stand here as a proud supporter of NewJeans, a group that has captured our hearts and inspired countless fans worldwide. Their passion, creativity, and unique charm remind us all of the power of music to bring people together.

NewJeans is more than just a group; they are a symbol of innovation, determination, and authenticity in an ever-evolving industry. Each member has shown us that hard work, courage, and staying true to oneself can create something truly special.

As fans, it's our privilege to witness their journey, to celebrate their successes, and to cheer them on through every challenge. Together, we form a family that supports and uplifts one another, just as NewJeans uplifts us with their talent and energy.

To the members of NewJeans: thank you for sharing your music, your stories, and your dreams with us. We are here for you, every step of the way, and we can't wait to see what you achieve next.

Let’s continue to show our unwavering love and support for NewJeans as they shine even brighter. Fighting, NewJeans!
